%% Flow F & G — Equal split and custom amount
flowchart TD
    START([Participant in payment lobby]) --> MODE{Choose split mode}

    MODE -->|Equal| F1[Select participant subset]
    F1 --> F2[Preview: pool ÷ N with cent rounding]
    F2 --> F3{Confirm equal split?}
    F3 -->|no| START
    F3 -->|yes| FE[Emit split.equal.created]

    MODE -->|Custom| G1[Enter amount €]
    G1 --> G2{€0.50 ≤ amount ≤ remaining?}
    G2 -->|no min| MIN[CUSTOM_BELOW_MINIMUM]
    G2 -->|no max| CAP[Cap to remaining CUSTOM_EXCEEDS_REMAINING]
    G2 -->|ok| G3[Preview: pays toward shared pool]
    G3 --> GE[Emit split.custom.intent_created]

    MODE -->|Claimed items| E1[Use Flow E totals]
    E1 --> CHECKOUT

    FE --> CHECKOUT[Flow I: Tip → Checkout]
    GE --> CHECKOUT
    CAP --> CHECKOUT

    subgraph Rounding["Equal split example"]
        R1["Remainder €18.00 ÷ 4 = €4.50 each"]
    end

    style MIN fill:#f66
    style CHECKOUT fill:#9cf
